Plastisols are segmented by type, application, and end-user industry. In terms of type, PVC plastisols, phthalate-free plastisols, and non-phthalate plastisols are the key segments. Each type caters to specific needs and preferences in different applications. When considering application, plastisols are used in coating, moldings, screen printing, and various other processes. The versatility of plastisols allows for a wide range of applications across industries. Lastly, the end-user segmentation includes textile, automotive, construction, and other sectors that rely on plastisols for different purposes.

